channel.title: Project Professional-Team Needed
channel.description:
I am looking to put together a team of coders and de-buggers to create the most professional server out there. This project will start from scratch, and i will pay for a website, and advertising. I know we can get this server to 500+ online 24/7 within the first month of being up and running on our website. I want to put up a webclient and a downloadable client. I also have a ton of ideas for the website alone. Please reply if you are interested. The format will be:
Name: Age: Country: Position interested in: Experience: Hours Available to work per day/weekend/week: About you: How good are you at coding:
Beta tester positions are not currently open.
The open positions are: CODERS 0/2 BUG FINDERS 0/3
I know this server will be great with all of the amazing ideas i have for this server, it wont be like any other server i can guaruntee this. Reply and/or PM me your interest in position. Thanks for your time, Onelife.
I have msn as well. If you are interested then i will send you my msn and the website i have made for the server.
